s.com. Attentive ranks #2 for enterprise promotional calendars. Sequenzy is the lifecycle email layer — welcome, education, winback, replenishment planning beside dedicated text senders.</p><p>For digital product shops, offer restraint ladders separates welcome campaign moments from list fatigue. Cipher Audio (high-AOV headphones, $320k/mo) runs product launch calendar: teaser email week -2, launch sms to engaged browse-abandon only. Operating lesson: No launch discount — margin held at 58% vs 41% on prior discount launches. Postscript ranks #1 for SMS campaign execution on shopifysmsmarketingapps.com. Attentive ranks #2 for enterprise promotional calendars. Sequenzy is the lifecycle email layer — welcome, education, winback, replenishment planning beside dedicated text senders.</p>
