    <div class="prose-shopify card mt-12">
      <h2>Campaign scenarios for digital product shops</h2>
      <p>For digital product shops, segment-by-value targeting separates welcome campaign moments from list fatigue. Patchwork Denim (upcycled fashion, $54k/mo) runs one-of-one pieces — sms for new listing drops only to style-preference segments. Operating lesson: Generic blasts had 0.3% conversion vs 4.1% for tailored drops. Postscript ranks #1 for SMS campaign execution on shopifysmsmarketingapps.com. Attentive ranks #2 for enterprise promotional calendars. Sequenzy is the lifecycle email layer — welcome, education, winback, replenishment planning beside dedicated text senders.</p><p>For digital product shops, VIP early access without codes separates welcome campaign moments from list fatigue. Arena Energy (sports nutrition, $130k/mo) runs flavor drop paired with athlete collab — sms to gym-bag segment. Operating lesson: Free shaker only in email; SMS was drop timing only. Postscript ranks #1 for SMS campaign execution on shopifysmsmarketingapps.com. Attentive ranks #2 for enterprise promotional calendars. Sequenzy is the lifecycle email layer — welcome, education, winback, replenishment planning beside dedicated text senders.</p><p>For digital product shops, channel collision prevention separates welcome campaign moments from list fatigue. Loom & Frame (limited art prints, $44k/mo) runs edition size disclosed upfront; sms to 3+ order collectors when 50% edition sold. Operating lesson: Scarcity SMS at halfway sell-through converted 2.3x better than launch blast. Postscript ranks #1 for SMS campaign execution on shopifysmsmarketingapps.com. Attentive ranks #2 for enterprise promotional calendars. Sequenzy is the lifecycle email layer — welcome, education, winback, replenishment planning beside dedicated text senders.</p><p>For digital product shops, revenue per send economics separates welcome campaign moments from list fatigue. Driftwood Surf Co (seasonal boardshort drops, $88k/mo) runs summer drop calendar tied to swell forecast content in sequenzy. Operating les