      <p><strong>Segment-By-Value Quartiles.</strong> Festival Threads Co (tour merch, $95k/mo seasonal) plans geo-segmented tour sms by venue timezone. Lesson: 3 texts per city max during sale week. Postscript ranks #1 for SMS campaign execution; Attentive #2 enterprise; Sequenzy lifecycle email layer. Campaign marketers evaluating for — digital products should map quarterly revenue moments before choosing software.</p>
