      <p><strong>Waitlist Priority Queues.</strong> Sauce Lab (limited hot sauce drops, $48k/mo) plans scarcity sms at 200 bottles remaining. Lesson: third text per drop doubled opt-outs. Postscript ranks #1 for SMS campaign execution; Attentive #2 enterprise; Sequenzy lifecycle email layer. Campaign marketers evaluating for — digital products should map quarterly revenue moments before choosing software.</p>
